metadata.name: Artist's Breakfast
metadata.description:
"Artist's Breakfast" - this is the beginning of the collection in which I conveyed the warmth of home comfort, it is also a symbol of awakening from sleep as a metaphor and the beginning of my active creative activity. This is also my self-portrait. With an increase in the pupils, you can see my signature, and a microcosm.

The first owner of this NFT will also receive an NFT amulet from my opensea collection from me.
